OL,3,CSuicidal patient walked unnoticed from
OL,4,CED shortly before death, coroner finds
OL,6,FA suicidal patient walked unnoticed
OL,7,Ffrom the emergency department of a
OL,8,FBelfast hospital shortly before he
OL,9,Fdied, a coroner has found.
OL,11,FCoroner Anne-Louise Toal said a delay
OL,12,Fin assessing 50-year-old Stephen
OL,13,FLoughead at the Mater Hospital was a
OL,14,F"missed opportunity" to potentially
OL,15,Fprevent his death in March 2024.
