OL,3,CSuicidal patient walked unnoticed from
OL,4,CED shortly before death, coroner finds
OL,6,FThe coroner said Mr Loughead from
OL,7,Fnorth Belfast should have been
OL,8,Fassessed by a doctor within 10
OL,9,Fminutes, but instead was not called
OL,10,Ffor two hours, by which time he had
OL,11,Falready left the hospital.
OL,13,FMs Toal delivered her findings in the
OL,14,Finquest at Belfast Coroner's Court on
OL,15,FTuesday.
OL,17,FShe told the court that Mr Loughead
OL,18,Fhad attended Musgrave PSNI station in
OL,19,Fthe early hours of March 15 2024 and
OL,20,Fwas "clearly experiencing
OL,21,Fdeteriorating mental health".
