OL,3,CSuicidal patient walked unnoticed from
OL,4,CED shortly before death, coroner finds
OL,6,FThe coroner said police took him to
OL,7,Fthe emergency department of the Mater
OL,8,FHospital but did not accompany him
OL,9,Finside.
OL,11,FMs Toal said this action was "contrary
OL,12,Fto the joint guidance" between police
OL,13,Fand hospitals.
OL,15,FHowever, she said the failure to
OL,16,Faccompany him to ED did not alter the
OL,17,Fway in which he was treated.
OL,19,FMs Toal said Mr Loughead waited more
OL,20,Fthan an hour to be triaged, in excess
OL,21,Fof the target time of 15 minutes.
