OL,3,CSuicidal patient walked unnoticed from
OL,4,CED shortly before death, coroner finds
OL,6,FThe coroner said: "Due to staffing
OL,7,Fpressures, it was not possible to
OL,8,Fclosely monitor him as was appropriate
OL,9,Fand as a result it is unknown what
OL,10,Ftime he left the department, other
OL,11,Fthan it was after he was last seen at
OL,12,F7.30am."
OL,14,FMs Toal said that as Mr Loughead was
OL,15,Frecognised as being "actively
OL,16,Fsuicidal", he should then have been
OL,17,Fseen by a doctor within 10 minutes.
