OL,3,CSuicidal patient walked unnoticed from
OL,4,CED shortly before death, coroner finds
OL,6,FShe said: "Due to chronic severe
OL,7,Fpressures existing within the ED, he
OL,8,Fwas not called for another two hours,
OL,9,Fby which time he had left the
OL,10,Femergency department unnoticed.
OL,12,F"I find the environment in the
OL,13,Femergency department and the
OL,14,Fprotracted wait in a noisy and busy
OL,15,Funit exacerbated his condition and
OL,16,Fcontributed to his leaving the
OL,17,Fdepartment before being assessed and
OL,18,Fthis represents a missed opportunity
OL,19,Fto treat the deceased's suicidal
OL,20,Fideation at that time."
