OL,3,CSuicidal patient walked unnoticed from
OL,4,CED shortly before death, coroner finds
OL,6,FThe coroner said it was not possible
OL,7,Ffor her to say if the patient would
OL,8,Fhave been detained at the hospital if
OL,9,Fhe had been assessed earlier.
OL,11,FBut she added: "I do find there was a
OL,12,Fmissed opportunity to assess him in a
OL,13,Ftimely manner, which may have
OL,14,Fprevented his leaving the emergency
OL,15,Fdepartment on that day and the tragic
OL,16,Fevents that followed."
OL,18,FThe coroner said emergency department
OL,19,Fstaff are in an "unenviable position".
