OL,3,CSuicidal patient walked unnoticed from
OL,4,CED shortly before death, coroner finds
OL,6,FShe said: "It is a stark reality that,
OL,7,Fas per the evidence heard by this
OL,8,Finquest, was the deceased to walk into
OL,9,Fthe Mater ED today, it is unlikely
OL,10,Fthat anything would change in the way
OL,11,Fthat he was dealt with, not due to a
OL,12,Flack of want or care, but due to a
OL,13,Fchronic lack of resources in a milieu
OL,14,Fof increasing pressures."
OL,16,FThe coroner said Mr Loughead was last
OL,17,Fseen by nursing staff at the morning
OL,18,Fhandover at 7.30am and at some point
OL,19,Fin the next hour he left the hospital
OL,20,Fand travelled towards the city centre.
