OL,6,FShe said Mr Loughead was later seen in
OL,7,Fthe River Lagan after 9am.
OL,9,FDespite a rescue operation, Mr
OL,10,FLoughead died in the Royal Victoria
OL,11,FHospital from hypoxic brain injury
OL,12,Fcaused by cardiac arrest as a result
OL,13,Fof drowning.
OL,15,FThe coroner passed on her condolences
OL,16,Fto the family before closing the
OL,17,Finquest.
